race.comment: JAMAICA RUM (6) has missed the placings at his last couple but was in the money three back when second (19.77) at this track in a Grade 5. Look for sharp improvement here. WRANGLER FUSION (8) showed little early speed at his last couple, the latest finishing fourth (18.85) in a Grade 5 at Dubbo. Has ability and a bold showing is expected. DALAIR JESS (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing fourth (20.04) last time in a Grade 5 at this track. Great chance to atone. Something for the Multiples: FIERY CHANA (1)
